## Summary
This documentation explains how to integrate Slack with Amplitude, allowing users to receive Amplitude updates in Slack channels, view expanded previews of charts and dashboards, receive notifications about comments, and connect Team Spaces to specific Slack channels for real-time updates on new analytics content and tracking plan changes.

